media:group.media:title: The Twin Algorithms
media:group.media:description:
This will be a live presentation of my CppNorth 2022 talk entitled "The Twin Algorithms" presented previously on July 20. We will take a look at how and why a C++ developer fell in love with APL and how it affects the way you can solve problems in C++ and in other programming languages.
